@startuml
skinparam style strictuml

actor "Admin" as Admin
participant "ReportPanel\n(View)" as View
participant "ReportController" as Controller
participant "ReportService" as Service
database "MySQL\n(BoardingHouse_DB)" as DB

Note over Admin, DB: QUY TRÌNH TỔNG HỢP DOANH THU

Admin -> View : 1. Chọn thời gian thống kê
View -> Controller : 2. getRevenueReport(startDate, endDate)
activate Controller

Controller -> Service : 3. calculateTotalRevenue(startDate, endDate)
activate Service

Service -> DB : 4. SELECT SUM(tong_tien) FROM HOA_DON WHERE da_thanh_toan = TRUE
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 5. Doanh thu từ hóa đơn
deactivate DB

Service -> DB : 6. SELECT SUM(so_tien) FROM BOI_THUONG WHERE da_thu = TRUE
activate DB
DB -->> Service : 7. Doanh thu từ bồi thường
deactivate DB

Service -> Service : 8. Tổng hợp dữ liệu & Phân loại theo hinh_thuc

Service -->> Controller : 9. Report Data (JSON/Object)
deactivate Service

Controller -->> View : 10. Render chart & tables
deactivate Controller

View -->> Admin : 11. Hiển thị biểu đồ doanh thu
@enduml